'''诺埃米·托马斯'''（{{lang|en|Noemie Thomas}}，{{bd|1996年|2月4日||}}）生于不列颠哥伦比亚省列治文，是一名加拿大女子游泳运动员，主攻蝶泳<ref>{{cite web|url=https://olympic.ca/team-canada/noemie-thomas/|title=Noemie Thomas|work=[[加拿大奥林匹克委员会|Canadian Olympic Comittee]]|accessdate=2020-07-18|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190627201819/https://olympic.ca/team-canada/noemie-thomas/|archivedate=2019-06-27|dead-url=no}}</ref>，曾就读于加利福尼亚大学柏克莱分校<ref>{{cite web|url=https://calbears.com/sports/womens-swimming-and-diving/roster/noemie-thomas/11669|title=Noemie Thomas|work=Cal Bears|accessdate=2020-07-18|archiveurl=https://archive.today/20200718021811/https://calbears.com/sports/womens-swimming-and-diving/roster/noemie-thomas/11669|archivedate=2020-07-18|dead-url=no}}</ref>。她在5岁时开始接触游泳，7岁时开始练习竞技游泳。她在童年时期也曾练习过[[芭蕾舞|芭蕾舞]]，12岁时，她决定放弃芭蕾舞，将最主要的精力投入到游泳上<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.swimmingworldmagazine.com/news/graceful-noemie-thomas-focused-on-title-finish/|title=Graceful Noemie Thomas Focused on Title Finish for Cal|publisher=Swimming World Magazine|date=2018-02-08|accessdate=2020-07-18|archiveurl=https://archive.today/20200718021222/https://www.swimmingworldmagazine.com/news/graceful-noemie-thomas-focused-on-title-finish/|archivedate=2020-07-18|dead-url=no}}</ref>。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.fina.org/athletes/noemie-thomas|title=Noemie Thomas|work=[[国际游泳联合会|FINA]]|accessdate=2020-07-18|archiveurl=https://archive.today/20200718020856/https://www.fina.org/athletes/noemie-thomas|archivedate=2020-07-18|dead-url=no}}</ref>

